Join us for our Nathan Jess Worship Concert 
 Hope Church Malta  (http://hopechurchmalta.com) is  excited to announce that Nathan Jess (http://www.nathanjess.com/home.html) a worship leader, songwriter and recording artist from Ireland suported by Hope Worship is joining us for a not to missed worship concert on 12 December 2015 starting at 7pm till 9:30pm. The concert is a free event to bring friends and family along and kick off the feastive mood. It will feature other local worship teams as a build up to Nathan Jess.